heading: 2 Times the Fun (Ages 3 1/2 - 5)
alert_info: What you need to know: (1) This is a non-parented program. (2) All participants must be toilet trained. (3) There is no early drop-off or late pick-up for this program. (4) A $10.00 late fee will be charged to your account for every 15 minutes past pick-up time. (5) Registration forms will be required per camp for each child. Please allow yourself enough time on the first day of the program to ensure that we have all of the required information to ensure each child's safety. (6) Please notify your instructor of any allergies or health concerns relating to your child on the first day (7) Please send your child with a nut-free snack, water, socks, and closed toe shoes (preferably running shoes). Appropriate indoor and outdoor attire is needed for possible weather changes.

heading: Camp Olympics (6 - 7 Years)
alert_info:
What you need to know: (1) This camp includes early drop-off which starts at 8:00 am and late pick-up which goes up until 5:00 pm.(2) Please send your participant with nut-free snacks and lunch (due to ratio purposes we can NOT take children to the vendors on site to purchase a lunch), water, socks, and closed toe shoes (preferably running shoes). Appropriate indoor and outdoor attire is needed for possible weather changes. (3) A $10.00 late fee will be charged to your account for every 15 minutes past pick-up time. (4) Registration forms will be required per camp for each child. Please allow yourself enough time on the first day of camp to ensure that we have all of the required information to ensure each child's safety. (5) Please notify your instructor of any allergies or health concerns relating to each child on the first day of camp. 
There will be SWIMMING in the afternoons from Monday - Thursday in this camp. Your child will need a swimsuit and towel; as well as, a personal lock or $0.50 for a locker. 
This full-day camp is for children ages 6-12 yrs. Separate barcodes are for ratio purposes only. Each child must be registered under their actual age.

heading: Painting Flowers with Acrylics
crse_descr: Capturing the beauty of flowers in Acrylics is the focus of this class. Through demonstrations, learn to paint petals, leaves, and backgrounds using a variety of techniques. Several techniques, colour suggestions, and basic composition strategies will be included. You will complete this class not only with the know-how to continue painting flowers, but also with at least one finished painting.

heading: Painting Flowers with Watercolour
crse_descr: Capturing the beauty and translucence of flowers in watercolour is the focus of this class. Through demonstrations, learn to paint petals, leaves, and backgrounds using a variety of techniques. Several techniques, colour suggestions, and basic composition strategies will be included. You will complete this class not only with the know-how to continue painting flowers, but also with at least one finished painting.

heading: Painting: Studio Time
